    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a functional, budget-friendly option for someone looking for a reliable runner. While it starts and drives, it shows clear signs of age, including noticeable wear on the interior upholstery and several cosmetic blemishes like scratches and minor dings on the exterior. Mechanically, it is operational but will likely need some minor repairs and routine maintenance soon to keep it in peak shape. It's a solid choice for a commuter car if you don't mind a bit of character and some upcoming DIY projects.",
      "price": 19500.0,
