      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, reflecting a level of preservation rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, adheres to the most exacting standards of excellence. Mechanically superior and aesthetically peerless, this offering represents a singular opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection without compromise.",
      "price": 43500.0,
