    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem! \ud83c\udf1f It is in truly stunning shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I have babied this car since the day I got it, so you won't find a single mark on it. It drives like a total dream and has been kept tucked away in the garage. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show you around this beauty! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
